scoringPlays.text: Jake Ferguson 18 Yd pass from Jack Coan (Collin Larsh Kick)
Donny Navarro 48 Yd pass from Brandon Peters (James McCourt Kick)
Jonathan Taylor 5 Yd Run (Collin Larsh Kick)
Reggie Corbin 43 Yd Run (James McCourt Kick)
Josh Imatorbhebhe 29 Yd pass from Brandon Peters (James McCourt Kick)

videos.description: Jonathan Taylor becomes the third FBS player to reach 5,000 rushing yards before the end of his junior season.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Taylor surpasses 5,000 career rushing yards) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Taylor surpasses 5,000 career rushing yards

videos.description: Wisconsin quarterback Jack Coan throws a dart to tight end Jake Ferguson for the 18-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Coan ropes pass to Ferguson for the TD) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Coan ropes pass to Ferguson for the TD

videos.description: Illinois wide receiver Donny Navarro catches the pass, breaks a tackle, then takes off for the 48-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Navarro takes off for 48-yard Illinois TD) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Navarro takes off for 48-yard Illinois TD

videos.description: Jonathan Taylor weaves through the defense and gets into the end zone for the 5-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Taylor finds the end zone from 5 yards out) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Taylor finds the end zone from 5 yards out

videos.description: Illinois running back Reggie Corbin runs right by the Wisconsin defense for the 43-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Corbin flies to the end zone for the Illini TD) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Corbin flies to the end zone for the Illini TD

videos.description: Illinois gets back into the game with a 29-yard touchdown pass to Josh Imatorbhebhe.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Imatorbhebhe hauls in the Illinois TD) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Imatorbhebhe hauls in the Illinois TD

videos.description: Illinois completes a fourth quarter comeback as James McCourt hits a 39-yard field goal as time expires to upset Wisconsin 24-23.
videos.headline: Illinois upsets Wisconsin with 39-yard FG
